<% meta_description("Designing a website for flight schools is more than just showing a few pictures and leaving a contact form.  Your website is the ultimate sales tool to get new student pilots.  See what Right Rudder Marketing can do for your flight school.") %>

<!--Set Page font size and limit sticky-->
<div class="text-lg">
  <%= render "shared/navbar"%>

  <!--Header Section-->
